 (27,'Sport','http://talksport.com/football/liverpool-eye-next-summer-bargain-edging-closer-deal-goalkeeper-adam-bogdan-150605149686','Liverpool eye next summer bargain by edging closer to deal for goalkeeper Adam Bogdan

