 (57,'Fashion','http://feeds.glamour.com/c/35377/f/665038/s/46f1104f/sc/23/l/0L0Sglamour0N0Cfashion0Cblogs0Cdressed0C20A150C0A60Ckarlie0Ekloss0Ecrop0Etop0E49/story01.htm','Hey, Tall Girls: Karlie Kloss''s $49 Crop Top Is Designed Specifically for You

